{
  "stem": "20084.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "And you put them down there, because next step was always-- in Mauthausen-- was a heap the dead bodies overnight.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "They were piled up in such a-- like crisscross.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "The bodies were crisscross, laying 10, 12, 15 feet high, just from overnight what they died or they drown them, or whatever, whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "And then one of those, when I was thrown into the bathroom, this was already-- I was laying in the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "This was before you die.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "You-- they were putting you to the bathroom down there to the latrines.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the blockalteste came in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 96,
      "text": "And he saw me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 97,
      "text": "And he performed oral sex on me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 98,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I don't when I-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 99,
      "text": "I managed or what.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 100,
      "text": "And I, I wash myself up afterwards.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 101,
      "text": "And I came-- the following day, I went to work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 102,
      "text": "Sometimes in winter, we had to stay for hours and hours till we froze to death.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 103,
      "text": "People were freezing to death.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a lot of people were reporting to the sick bed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But who cared?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Who-- didn't care.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You never saw those people anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the war, we found out that they were, they were taken.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were taken and, and gassed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were taken in an ambulance and gassed on the way somewhere.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were gassed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we, we didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This, we found out after the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anyhow, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the blockaltestes, the murderers, the whatever they were, if they wanted-- let's say there were 400 people on the-- in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If they wanted extra rations for themself, they could kill a few people so they have more bread, or soup, or whatever for themself.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
